text:
BN TV: Super-Easy Pre-Curled Crochet Braids and Protective Styles with Nicola 11.01.2017 at By BN TV Leave a Comment 
In this video, Nicola , does a review of these pre-curled crochet braids. She shares her review about the hair, hair installation and protective styles. She said; 
“I am really excited about this hair because you don’t have to deep it in hot water, it is pre-curled. Its like the perfect crochet hair!”
